  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice — factual stub, not your words. Draft until ready. -->\n<p class=\"\">A terminal reflex game for training your eye to spot differences: two values flash up, you call them <em class=\"\">Different</em> or <em class=\"\">Same</em> as fast as you can — and the system is watching the clock.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"CLI Delta Dojo title screen\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/cli-delta-dojo/title.png\" alt=\"CLI Delta Dojo title screen\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/cli-delta-dojo/title.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/cli-delta-dojo/title.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/cli-delta-dojo/title.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/cli-delta-dojo/title.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"CLI Delta Dojo title screen\" width=\"1200\" height=\"700\" style=\"--splay-rot:-2.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1200×700\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-video w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">CLI Delta Dojo title screen</figcaption>\n</figure>",
